This topic describes how you can configure the BOSH Director on Azure Government Cloud.

To begin, follow the steps in [Preparing to deploy <%= vars.ops_manager %> on Azure](prepare-env-manual.html) and [Deploying <%= vars.ops_manager %> on Azure](deploy-manual.html).

Then, follow the manual Azure installation procedure in [Configuring BOSH Director on Azure](config-manual.html). In the procedure, click **Azure Government Cloud** in the **Azure Environment** drop-down menu and set custom VM types.
